caller_intent: Cecilia is seeking help to resolve two issues: (1) deleting a booking page she created and (2) locating a missing email reply from LightSpeedVoice to an email sent on September 9th.
resolution_steps: Agent acknowledges the booking issue but defers resolution until Cecilia can provide more details later.
Agent confirms the email was sent to LightSpeedVoice on September 9th and agrees to perform a message trace to locate the missing reply.
Agent requests Cecilia to call back when available to proceed with the message trace.
knowledge_required: Message trace procedures for email recovery
summary: Cecilia contacted Stephen to address a booking deletion issue and a missing email reply from LightSpeedVoice. The agent agreed to perform a message trace to locate the email but required Cecilia to call back later for follow-up. The booking issue was deferred for further clarification.
